iscretization based on dual boundary elements residing on a suitably defined\ndual mesh. Finally we show how the resulting EEG problems has favorable\nproperties with respect to previously proposed schemes and we show their\napplicability to real case modeling scenarios obtained from MRI data.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 20 Mar 2016 22:41:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-03-22"}
